To upgrade OLAS from verion 2.2 to version 2.2.1:

- The directory 20140515220005 should be placed under the existing
  releases directory

- Verify that the symbolic link for log/ resolves to the shared/log/ directory

- Verify that the file config/databases.yml resolves to the existing version
  in the shared/config/ directory

- No database updates are required

- Change the symbolic link "current" to point to releases/20140515220005
